a gang of psychopathic killers.

193
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:33,480
I tried to kill Jim Gordon
and Lee Thompkins.

194
00:11:33,560 --> 00:11:34,640
I was a puppet...

195
00:11:35,720 --> 00:11:37,240
Of these demons in my head

196
