to do these terrible things.

197
00:11:43,720 --> 00:11:46,400
I wish I could go back
and undo what I've done.

198
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,760
Only I can't.

199
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,840
I don't feel insane...

200
