Thank you, Barbara.

204
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,320
That was very brave.

205
00:12:11,440 --> 00:12:15,640
What do you suppose
made this helpful change in you?

206
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,320
Maybe I just...

207
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:22,160
Really needed some sleep.

208
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,240
It's a good act.

209
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:36,680
So, sure it's an act are you?

210
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:40,760
- Aren't you?
- I have no idea.

211
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:44,720
One way or the other,
she intrigues me.

212
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:47,600
Well, if you would allow us
to apply rigorous dream therapy,

213
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:50,080
- we would know for sure...
- No, no, no.

214
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:55,440
We do have very useful hammer,
Ms. Peabody,

215
00:12:55,520 --> 00:12:59,160
but not all of our patients
are nails.

216
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:19,080
Thank you.

217
00:13:19,160 --> 00:13:21,120
What the hell happened last night?

218
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,320
Stumbled onto a mugging.

219
00:13:24,400 --> 00:13:27,280
And Jim Gordon couldn't just walk by.

220
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:32,040
- Where'd you sleep?
- Didn't. Just walked around.

221
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:34,760
- How's Barnes?
- He's on the warpath.

222
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:37,080
Governor announced
a 10,000-dollar reward

223
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:39,000
for anyone who helps catch you.

224
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:41,760
Ten thousand? You should turn me in.

225
00:13:41,840 --> 00:13:44,960
If he doubled that to 20?
I'll give it some thought.

226
00:13:45,040 --> 00:13:47,000
- Okay, here.
- <i>Internal Affairs.</i>

227
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:51,880
<i>I, I want to report a crime.</i>

228
00:13:51,960 --> 00:13:54,880
- You recognize that voice?
- Sounds like it's been disguised.

229
00:13:56,040 --> 00:14:00,080
<i>I saw Detective James Gordon
shooting Mayor Theo Galavan.</i>

230
00:14:00,160 --> 00:14:02,120
<i>On the Southside Docks.</i>

231
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:04,440
<i>The Penguin was beating him
with a bat,</i>

232
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,880
