that pulled the trigger.</i>

233
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,400
Is that a bird?

234
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,320
Run it back.

235
00:14:19,400 --> 00:14:22,000
We gotta find somebody
to clean up the tape.

236
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:25,320
Isolate the sound.
Maybe do something to the voice.

237
00:14:26,800 --> 00:14:28,640
I gotta get going.

238
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,480
Barnes is watching me like a hawk.

239
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,200
All right.

240
00:14:32,280 --> 00:14:33,520
Hey.

241
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:35,560
You've done more
than any partner could ask.

242
00:14:35,640 --> 00:14:39,200
From now on, stay away from me.
For your own sake.

243
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,280
If Loeb was behind this,

244
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,400
